OL,3,CGrandfather accused of toddler's
OL,4,Cmurder says boy's mother was 'quick-
OL,5,Ctempered'
OL,7,FA man accused of murdering his
OL,8,Fgrandson has told a court the
OL,9,Ftoddler's mother was "quick-tempered"
OL,10,Fand would slap him to the back of the
OL,11,Fhead.
OL,13,FMichael Ives, 47, and his wife Kerry,
OL,14,F46, are accused of fatally injuring
OL,15,Ftwo-year-old Ethan Ives-Griffiths when
OL,16,Fhe lived with them at their home in
OL,17,FGarden City, Flintshire, before his
OL,18,Fdeath on 16 August, 2021.
