OL,3,CGrandfather accused of toddler's
OL,4,Cmurder says boy's mother was 'quick-
OL,5,Ctempered'
OL,7,FWhile giving evidence at Mold Crown
OL,8,FCourt on Monday, 30 June, Ives said
OL,9,Fhis daughter, Shannon Ives, 28, would
OL,10,Fhit her son after they both moved into
OL,11,Ftheir home earlier that year.
OL,13,FHe said she was "quick-tempered" and
OL,14,Fwould slap him to the back of the
OL,15,Fhead, as well as to the legs or
OL,16,Fbackside.
OL,18,FAsked how often that would happen, he
OL,19,Fsaid: "Sometimes it would be a couple
OL,20,Fof times a day, but it just varied."
