OL,5,Ctempered'
OL,7,FHe told the court that his daughter
OL,8,Fwould hit the toddler so his head
OL,9,Fwould jolt forward, adding: "Ethan
OL,10,Fwould just stand there, look at her
OL,11,Fand just start laughing at her."
OL,13,FIves said his daughter would become
OL,14,Fmore angry after that reaction.
OL,16,FHe said that he told her she should
OL,17,Fnot hit Ethan, telling the court: "I
OL,18,Fdid pull her up on it." He said
OL,19,FShannon Ives would tell him to mind
OL,20,Fhis own business.
