OL,5,Ctempered'
OL,7,FWhen asked if he ever physically told
OL,8,FEthan off by hitting him or slapping
OL,9,Fhim, he said: "No."
OL,11,FHe told the court he was "protective"
OL,12,Fof Shannon when she was a teenager,
OL,13,Fbut said he had never hit any of his
OL,14,Fchildren.
OL,16,FThe court has heard that Ethan died in
OL,17,Fhospital two days after an ambulance
OL,18,Fwas called to the house, following
OL,19,Fwhat the prosecution allege was a
OL,20,F"forceful attack".
