OL,7,FEthan is alleged to have been targeted
OL,8,Fas an "object of abuse and neglect"
OL,9,Fduring his time at his grandparents'
OL,10,Fhome.
OL,12,FIves told the court that his own
OL,13,Fupbringing in Wolverhampton was a "bad
OL,14,Fone".
OL,16,FHe said he met his wife when he was 18
OL,17,Fand she gave birth to Shannon, their
OL,18,Feldest child, around a year later.
