OL,7,FThe couple moved between Wolverhampton
OL,8,Fand north Wales before settling in
OL,9,FGarden City in 2019, the court heard.
OL,11,FThe jury was told Ives received a
OL,12,Fpolice caution for assaulting his wife
OL,13,Fin 2009.
OL,15,FHe said: "We had an argument and I
OL,16,Fwent to kick the coffee table and I
OL,17,Fmissed and caught her leg."
