OL,7,FMichael and Kerry Ives, of Kingsley
OL,8,FRoad, Garden City, deny murder, an
OL,9,Falternative count of causing or
OL,10,Fallowing the death of a child, and
OL,11,Fcruelty to a person under 16.
OL,13,FShannon Ives, of Nant Garmon, Mold,
OL,14,Fdenies causing or allowing the death
OL,15,Fof a child and cruelty to a person
OL,16,Funder 16.
